	nt their vision effectively. This class breaks down marketing and branding
	 into simple\, actionable steps-from creating a brand identity to crafting
	 a social media strategy. Students will discover how strong brands inspire
	 trust and attract community support. Key Takeaways:  Understand branding
	\, social media\, and marketing strategy.  Learn how to communicate a mis
	sion and connect with customers.  Activity: Create a logo\, tagline\, and
	 one-page marketing plan.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details
