UID:KngcF55a7mlRBaw4rOnyI
SUMMARY:ToDos Bike Garage -- Bike Repair Co-op
DTSTAMP:20260307T213103Z
DTSTART:20260315T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Come work on bikes on Sundays!  Please call/text ahead \\(323.9
	26.8054\\) to confirm ToDos Bike Garage will be open on a given Sunday. Vo
	lunteer run.  ToDos Bike Garage is open for bike repair\, tune-up\, and fl
	at fixes. We have all the basic bike tools and are ready to work on bikes 
	together! We're happy to teach you how to maintain your bike\, and help yo
	u get it working right. It's free to come work on your bike\, and we do ha
	ve some parts available\, but you may need to buy your own parts if someth
	ing comes up.  Follow @todos\\_garage on Instagram!\n\nhttps://seatoday.6a
	mcity.com/events/#/details/todos-bike-garage-bike-repair-co-op/18291157/20
	26-03-15T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Sports & Outdoors
